title: 11-year-old girl from British family shot dead in France
description: An 11-year-old girl from a British family has been shot dead in France.

title: Wedding bus crashes and overturns in Australia - killing 10 people
description: Ten people have been killed and 25 injured after a bus carrying wedding guests crashed in Australia.

description: For Manchester City and their fans - unbridled joy.
